    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Why Your Service Desk Needs Copilot Now"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Cut Ticket Triage Time by 70%"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Productivity Gained Every Day"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Lower Operational Costs"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Proactive  Service"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Service organizations that embrace generative AI today see faster resolution, lower operational costs, and higher customer satisfaction (CSAT) scores.",
        "The AI agent instantly analyzes, categorizes, and routes tickets, allowing human agents to start working on the issue immediately.\n\nRequest a call",
        "Folio3 Copilot reclaims valuable agent time from repetitive manual tasks, allowing your team to focus on complex problem-solving and proactive customer engagement.\n\nREQUEST A CALL",
        "AI automation reduces the dependency on large Tier 1 support teams and streamlines workflows, directly lowering your Cost-per-Contact.\n\nREQUEST A CALL",
        "Smart sentiment analysis allows the system to automatically prioritize critical or high-risk tickets, ensuring no angry customer is ever overlooked.\n\nREQUEST A CALL"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
